sellerCard.description: Hello, this is Ala Uddin. I'm a certified Website developer and designer with 4+ years of experience. I've expertise in WebFlow, WordPress, and GoDaddy platforms. Also, WebFlow CMS integration and interaction and animation specialist. I have built many websites on different platforms with user-friendly interfaces and responsiveness on all devices. I have worked from simple to complex but stunning website designs. All your Website solutions are here. Don't look for further contact now for a free consultation.

description.content:
Hi Fiverr Community,


Looking for a professional to design a Webflow website or need to improve your existing website design?


Then cheers! You are at the right gig.


With over 4 years of experience, I can design modern, clean, responsive Webflow sites for you. I care deeply about helping startups express their stories through design.


You will get a Webflow design to take your company to the next level.


This gig includes a complete professional Webflow design with the following features:


 High-converting Landing Page

 Modern, Professional, Responsive Layouts

 Design from Figma/sketch

 Responsive & SEO Friendly

 Fully Functional eCommerce

 Visually Attractive Layout

 Full Functional CMS

 Enhanced Security with Image Optimization


Why Choose Us?


Excellent Communication

 24/7 Online

 Unlimited Revisions

 Free Support for 30 Days


Youre just a step away from getting a professional Webflow website for your business. Order now!

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need to start my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You need to provide me with the following details. Specifications, Your Requirements, Backgrounds, Features you want, Data and Text, Webflow login credentials.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will the website be responsive across all devices?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! It will be responsive across all devices and browsers.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Where will you build the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will build your Webflow website in your Webflow account.

reviews.comment: The developer maintained professional politeness throughout our interaction, which I appreciated. However, the final deliverables fell short of expectations in several areas. The lack of attention to detail was evident in multiple instances - there were inconsistencies in formatting and several oversights in the project requirements that had been clearly outlined. While they responded promptly to messages, the work required significant revisions to meet the original specifications. The final result, even after feedback, didn't fully align with what we had initially discussed. Given these factors, I would suggest more thorough quality checks and closer adherence to project requirements.

seller_response.comment: Always fixed the issue as mentioned in the meeting discussion. Thank you for your detailed feedback I will implement in my projects. If you need any further help let me know I will work on them.

reviews.comment: If you're looking for a gorgeous marketing site to be built from scratch, you simply shouldn't look any further. Ala and his team delivered a stunning final product with multiple pages, dynamic icons, CTAs etc. without too much exact guidance on what it should look like or branding. If there were sections I didn't have any ideas in mind for, he and his team would get creative and suggest 2-3 different options that might fit well. These guys are pros, thank you!

Ala was incredible to work with. He and his team delivered an exceptional project considering the timeline and costs. I'm very picky with who I work with and the design I had them develop was a bit complicated. Ala was very communicative if he needed extra explanations or wanted to review details. I'm very very pleased with the final product and would definitely work with Ala again in the future. Incredible site development and nice attention to details in animations. Love it.

seller_response.comment: Thank you so much, Sarah! It was a pleasure working with you, and I truly appreciate your clear communication and trust throughout the project. We are always committed to assisting you with our best effort and expertise. Im thrilled youre happy with the final result and would love to collaborate again! I recommend her to everyone as a great buyer. Take care and best regards!

reviews.comment: He is exceptional in website development. Has a lot of great ideas and skills that helped make our design come to life. He was exceptionally quick in developing the complete site with all functionality within a very short time and was very helpful in making edits per our requests. Highly recommend!

1st) initially he did well but he started asking me questions about the other pages and after I answered with examples he still didn't get the work done. Then he asked for an extension which I asked why and he just replied he needed one. Then after I have him a 7 day extension I responded with detailed corrections and changes and then a day later he submitted delivery after receiving an extension with changes still not made.

seller_response.comment:
As agreed upon, the original order was for three pages, which I completed within the specified timeframe. Following your request for additional pages, I accommodated this by providing six pages at no extra cost.

When you inquired about further pages, I explained that the original requirements had been fulfilled, and any additional work would require an extra cost. Unfortunately, you chose to hire someone else for the task.

Anyway, If you need any further assistance in the future, please don't hesitate to reach out. My inbox is always open for you and I will be happy to help.
